metadata.name: Vieillesse
metadata.description:
During the Vodoo Festival, the Vodoo Devotees come together in different part of Benin and Togo to celebrate this festival in different shades; young and old, boys and girls-This portrait comes with so much power from her skin, eyesight, hair and the amazing beads adorned.

üìç Oiudah, Benin
January 2023
